thorities can create a false sense of security for those above the average or better than their neighbors. By emphasizing appropriate data use, LEAs are discouraged from becoming complacent and prompted to strive for continuous improvement in educational standards.&#10;5. Highlighting individual school impact: Proper data interpretation helps LEAs recognize the positive impact that individual schools have on their students, even if the overall authority performance may not be as strong. This focus on individual school success can inform best practices and inspire growth across the entire education system within the local authority.">
