ng a ring-fenced grant of £10 million for local authorities to support the education of minority ethnic children. By having a more sophisticated conversation about attainment across different subgroups, resources can be better targeted and help in understanding the differences within the diverse minority ethnic group (Speaker: Kirsty Williams AM).&#10;3. This approach will ensure that efforts are focused on addressing the root causes of underachievement among certain subgroups, ultimately leading to more equitable education outcomes for all students.">
