inister. The strategic delivery group is also considering a national service model with local accountability for monitoring and consistency purposes.&#10;&#10;As for the ERW (Education Through Regional Working) regional school improvement service, there are concerns about Neath Port Talbot's potential withdrawal from the consortium. While the Welsh Government does not intend to intervene directly, they seek clarification on Neath Port Talbot's plans to fulfill their functions in absence of ERW, especially considering the critical time for introducing the new curriculum. The government aims to ensure that schools and students are not disadvantaged without the support from ERW.">
